  "detailed_description": "You wake up with no knowledge of how you got where you are or what may have transpired. Play through a truly original story conjured up by the demented minds of Buffnerd Studios.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this horror/dark comedy game you must use your wits to unlock doors, break into computer systems, complete tasks, solve puzzles, and escape...all while avoiding certain death from some strange presence.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nToggle between 1st or 3rd person game play.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRun, jump, roll, crouch, climb, hide, and interact with items or objects.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDiscover and use items to restore stats and reveal clues.",
